snippet.textDisplay: I had dreads for about 4 years, just like the first girl. Mine may have been a LITTLE longer. I had to cut them off because they were so heavy after I'd wash them that I'd end up with a migraine for 2-3 DAYS. I loved them so much I still have them in a bag in a drawer...one day I'd like to re-lock my hair, but probably with smaller locks this time so they don't get so big and heavy so fast.
